SUMMARY:Father's Day Ol' Smokey Competition
DESCRIPTION:DADS\, THIS ONE’S FOR YOU!\nJoin us for Dadapalooza from 1–5 PM at the brewery\, an afternoon dedicated to all things Dad. We’ll have curated local vendors on-site selling dad goods\, cold beer flowing\, and plenty of questionable dad jokes.\nStarting at 2 PM\, dads will go head-to-head in a series of elite competitions including:\n-Burger Flipping Flair Contest\n– Best Dad Fit Competition\n– LEGO Walk\n– Speed Diaper Changing Challenge\nCompete for your chance to win awesome prizes including an Ol’ Smokey Grill\, a Cutthroat Barbers gift card\, a Eureka Heights gift card\, and of course… beer.\nBring your dad\, your baby daddy\, your grandpa\, your grill master\, or just your best pair of white New Balances. See y’all there.
URL:https://www.eurekaheights.com/event/fathers-day-ol-smokey-competition-2026-06-20/
LOCATION:Tap Room\, 941 W 18TH ST.\, Houston\, TX\, 77008\, United States
CATEGORIES:Tap Room
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://www.eurekaheights.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/27dc3964-a666-4874-9f09-dcb2652e7da0.png
END:VEVENT
