SUMMARY:Southern Smoke Dog Show
DESCRIPTION:Join the Houston Smoke as they put on their second annual Houston Smoke Dog Show! Think you and your K9 companion have what it takes to win over the judges and take home the trophies? Come see us Sunday June 28th for the 2026 Smokin’ Dog Pageant and see!\nOur 2nd annual team fundraiser is here! We will have plenty of raffle baskets up for grabs and even a fully loaded Rip-It Softball Swag Bag!
URL:https://www.eurekaheights.com/event/southern-smoke-dog-show-2026-06-28/
